DESCRIPTION:Because we're cool plus did a good job with the Spark.io Nights
 \, Instructables selected us for the Raspberry Pi Night in May!\n\nHere's w
 hat we get:\n\n(5) Raspberry Pis\n(5) Power supplies\n(5) microSD cards\n(5
 ) Adafruit Perma-Proto HAT for Pi Mini Kit\n(2) Adafruit Pi T-Cobbler Plus 
 Kits\n\nhttp://www.instructables.com/community/May-2015-Build-Night-with-Ra
 spberry-Pi-and-Adafrui/\n\nThe first 2 people who write an Instructable tha
 t gets Featured by an Instructables Editor win a Raspberry Pi!\n\nSpots are
  VERY limited. Send email to contact@bloominglabs.org to reserve one.\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20150407T005601Z
LOCATION:Bloominglabs
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Raspberry Pi Build Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
