 r local hackerspace--BloomingLabs--and other Arduino programmers to work on
  your own build\, get help\, or share ideas about larger projects. Arduino 
 kits and some accessories provided\, or bring your own. You will\, however\
 , need to bring your own laptop. Drop in. Age 12 and up\n
