CREATED:20180809T144200Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>Bloominglabs will be participating in the MCPL Fix-It Fair!
 <br><br>The Monroe County Public Library invites the community to bring in 
 an item for repair free of charge at our first ever Fix-It Fair! Local prof
 essionals and volunteers will provide repairs and be available to coach att
 endees interested in learning how to make their own fixes. Limit one item p
 er person please.<br><br><br>Bring in your broken:<br><br><br>●Small applia
 nces (lamps\, toasters\, etc.)<br><br>●Skateboards<br><br>●Bicycles&nbsp\;<
 br><br>●Stringed instruments<br><br>●Clothing or textiles&nbsp\;<br><br>●Bo
 oks<br><br>●Jewelry<br><br>●Toys<br><br><br>Staff from the Monroe County So
 lid Waste Management District also provide information on recycling in the 
 Atrium and host talks on "Growing Green Households: Recycling 101" (1 PM) a
 nd "Growing Green Businesses And The Triple Bottom Line: People\, Planet\, 
 Profit" (3PM).<br><br><br><a href="https://mcpl.evanced.info/signup/EventDe
 tails?EventId=61178&amp\;backTo=Calendar&amp\;startDate=2018/08/09">MCPL Ev
 ent</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20180818T184159Z
LOCATION:Monroe County Public Library\, 303 E Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, 
 IN 47408\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Fix-It Fair
TRANSP:OPAQUE
